data.description:
Beautiful 2-story Texas Hill Country 5 bedroom home/3.5 baths! With 3,452 sq ft, this home features a 2 car garage, TWO primary bedrooms, study/office room and two car garage! Master bathroom in the downstairs room includes a grand bath with separate garden tub & shower & is completed by an extensive primary closet! Great for family living & entertaining, its open layout offers plentiful space for whatever a family needs!! MASSIVE 2nd-story living area is great for the family to gather, game or movie watch! Each bedroom has it's own unique layout with ample walk-in closet space. Don't miss the vast private backyard with enormous covered patio. A tastefully created 2nd patio area with firepit is perfect for large gatherings, cookouts & entertaining! 

1.5 times the monthly rent for the security deposit or ask us about our alternative security deposit which conveniently allows monthly payments. 

Pets negotiable.

Don't hesitate to schedule a viewing.

All tenants are automatically enrolled in our Tenant Benefit Package, which includes HVAC filter delivery every 60 days, on-demand pest control, general liability protection, utility concierge services, one-click payments and more!
